fundamentals of the Talk Now program by including more activities and adding diction. The second CD also included a voice recording suite, but we found this difficult to use. This recording software didn&#39;t even include a comparison to correct Spanish pronunciation.","Talk to Me combines the fundamentals of Talk Now and World Talk in lessons on pronunciation and dialogue.","The interactive picture dictionary allows you to easily explore over 2,000 words in Spanish. In this dictionary, there are picture association techniques including images, illustrations, video clips and other memory-enhancing tools that make retaining vocabulary simple.","The last product offered in the package is the Who Is Oscar Lake? program. The Oscar Lake program plunges you directly into a foreign city where you must solve a puzzling mystery in a new language. The Oscar Lake program allows you to explore the Spanish language through sight, sound and action-an entertaining and powerful way to teach."]},"id":"52eeed41-fe91-46be-8f4a-37e4d0d56874","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Learning Versatility"},"id":"b0c4e646-9c24-45b9-bab8-e1a295124d6d","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["There are five different programs you must learn to navigate and install. The navigation was relatively easy for each program. You must transition from one program to the next and learn to use each program and feature separately. This is awkward until you become familiar with all of the programs&#39; capabilities."]},"id":"15099c50-25a3-4b8b-94c2-f5cfd8616351","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Teaching Tools"},"id":"3f43cea4-2bb7-4ec9-9bfe-ac9f7643c8a8","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Installation was a little confusing because during the process we were asked which language we wanted the product installed. The question refers to the language you want to use to navigate the software (English) not the language you want to learn (Spanish). You must also install multiple programs, but the process was fairly simple."]},"id":"e280c606-2343-47c3-a12b-d309749735c4","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"03b68708-47a7-401f-8a25-b9a376028bca","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Instant Immersion is a combination of older versions of popular Spanish language software combined in one package. Although many vital areas of Spanish learning are covered, the programs are outdated. Consider purchasing current software for your language-learning needs."]},"id":"b4483876-797c-47e6-b659-fcea50677dab","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_681","url":"/instant-immersion-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"billy-bommer","url":"/author/billy-bommer","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Billy Bommer","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"bxro6Nv6xNbugJrSbgckh8","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","datePublished":"2018-09-24T23:10:00Z","name":"Instant Immersion Express Spanish","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","review":{"rating":52,"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","language":"en","dateModified":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","id":"gsStapqZj6mSAtbZHjZ9Qg","meta":{"title":"Instant Immersion Express Spanish Review 2017 | Spanish","description":" *Instant Immersion Express is still available but we decided not to update the review on this product because TOPICS Entertainment produces a more complete Spanish learning package, Instant"},"products":[{"slug":"instant-immersion-express-spanish","url":"/product/instant-immersion-express-spanish","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T21:50:05Z","name":"Instant Immersion Express Spanish","dateModified":"2019-04-17T21:50:05Z","id":"mfidUFJkbeLBeJutPPz3rM","dateImported":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateI